article_id:3026,category_name:News,title_name:Gala Dragalia Is Coming Soon!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia starts on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1656482400"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■What Are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><br></div><div>▼Featured adventurer:</div><div>5★ Gala Zena (light/staff)</div><div><br></div><div>▼Featured dragons:</div><div>5★ Gala Reborn Jeanne (light)</div><div>5★ Gala Thor (light)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1656482400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1656914399"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the featured adventurer and dragons below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer:</div><div>
