			<dd><div>Restores HP to all teammates, increases<br>their strength, and creates a healing zone.</div><div class="skill-detail">Recovery Potency: 108<br>Healing Zone Potency: 54<br>Skill Energy Required: 5,850<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 17,550<br>Special Effects:<br>・Strength +15%<br>　Lasts 60 seconds<br>　Does not stack<br></div></dd><dt
