			</dt>
			<dd><div>Deals damage to multiple targets and enemies<br>near those targets and increases the rate at<br>which the user's force strikes charge.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 50 × 5 hits<br>Damage: 350 × 5 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 8,775<br>Special Effects:<br>・Force Strike Rate +30%<br>　Lasts 15 seconds<br>　Does not stack<br></div></dd></dl></div>
