				<span>Thor's Hammer</span>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Deals damage to the target and nearby enemies,<br>and inflicts paralysis. Continually tapping the screen<br>while charging the attack will increase damage,<br>with damage reaching its maximum potential at<br>stage three. The attack will be unleashed after a<br>set time or upon reaching stage three.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 1,780 × 1 hit (MAX)<br>Special Effects:<br>・Paralysis<br>　Lasts 26 seconds<br>　Triggers every 3.9 seconds<br>　Damage: 44.2</div></dd></dl></div><div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/212bea9478466c5e63454315256b6a5f2.png"></span><span>(Light) Chariot Rider V</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Light: <br>increases strength by 50%, increases the user's<br>energy level by one stage for every 5 seconds<br>that pass, and provides a further increase to<br>the user's strength based on the user's<br>energy level, up to a maximum of 45%<br>when the user is energized.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/3a59dbd2051c2865bdfc9245c709a80a2.png"></span><span>(Light) Thunder Bringer II</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Light: <br>When the user's shapeshift is undone,<br>energizes the entire team.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>・The stats shown here represent the dragons at level 100, maximum bond, and unbound to the fourth stage. They do not represent the stats when first obtained.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div>2. An Alberian Battle Royale skin for the adventurer featured in this summon showcase will go on sale and will cost fewer items to unlock. Note that some adventurers do not have adventurer skins.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1656396000,update_time1648556165